This problem seems to be only with the CUDNN version not the CUNN version as all of the THCUNN and THNN *Convolution functions have a *Convolution_shapeCheck function.
Maybe the checks for CUDNN can go in the Convolution constructor in pytorch/torch/csrc/cudnn/Conv.cpp?
